boxed::Box::<T>::new_uninit.doc:
Constructs a new box with uninitialized contents.

# Examples

```
let mut five = Box::<u32>::new_uninit();
// Deferred initialization:
five.write(5);
let five = unsafe { five.assume_init() };

assert_eq!(*five, 5)
```

